'''黑根铁筷子'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Helleborus niger''}}）为[[毛茛科|毛茛科]][[铁筷子属|铁筷子属]]下的一个[[物种|物种]]，因冬季开花而俗称'''聖誕玫瑰'''。<ref name="theplantlist">[http://www.theplantlist.org/tpl1.1/record/kew-2844780 ''Helleborus niger'' L.]. In: ''The Plant List'' (2013). Version 1.1. Published on the Internet; http://www.theplantlist.org/ {{Wayback|url=http://www.theplantlist.org/ |date=20190523171514 }} [2014-8-25].</ref>种加词意思是“黑色的”，指的是它的根部颜色。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The dark side of the Christmas Rose|url=https://www.rhs.org.uk/education-learning/blogs/libraries/December-2016/hellebores|accessdate=2019-10-17|author=Briggs, Gill|date=2016-12-23|format=|publisher=The Royal Horticultural Society|language=|archive-date=2019-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191017174055/https://www.rhs.org.uk/education-learning/blogs/libraries/December-2016/hellebores|dead-url=no}}</ref>欧洲古代称之为'''黑嚏根草'''，与白嚏根草（[[藜芦属|藜芦属]]植物）相对。

